        "class": "ital",
        "text": "in mediam rem",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " (comp. Zunz, as above, p. 353). Grotius well says: “Hoc exordio usus Jesus explicavit prophetae locum et explicando implevit.”",
